cu.explanation_en: Setting the ciphering algorithm to the unknown enum 'nea9' will cause negotiation failure during the security negotiation phase and NAS registration rejection.

du.explanation_en: Setting dl_carrierBandwidth to an out-of-range value (1000) will cause invalid downlink carrier configuration and cell setup failure.
du.explanation_zh: 將 dl_carrierBandwidth 設定為超出範圍的值 (1000)，會導致無效的下行載波配置，並造成小區設定失敗。
